text: Vora Mackintosh (2 June 1929 - 30 April 1998) was a British alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1952 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:1998 deaths Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1952 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from London
